Hentai Researcher here, time to explain if this doujin should be tagged "amputee" or not.

Firstly, an amputee is considered to be "A person who has had one or more limbs removed by amputation."
Amputation being defined as "Surgical removal of all or part of a limb, an organ, or projecting part or process of the body.
;Traumatic or spontaneous loss of a limb, organ, or part."

Although these definitions typically apply to humans, and since real humans do not possess actual horns, 
we can simply ASSUME that the horns on Ganyu can be considered as a "Appendage" or an external body part of Ganyu.

Therefore, the removal of said part can be considered as an amputation, hence amputee. 
Although an amputee usually refers to individuals without limbs, 
Nhentai doesn't have that specific of a tagging system,
 and hence it'd just be classified under amputee tag.
